event.title: became a chartered city on 18 June 1960

data.event: Toledo became a chartered city on 18 June 1960 under Republic Act No. 2688.
Toledo City comprises 38 barangays: Toledo City came from Old Hinulawan (now called Daanglungsod) and New Hinulawan.

event.title: June 3, 1863 a series of earthquakes shook

data.event: On June 3, 1863 a series of earthquakes shook Hinulawan.
